oldCode:
ExecutorService exec =
    Executors.newFixedThreadPool(10);
try {
    futures = tasks.stream()
        .map(t -> exec.submit(t))
        .toList();
} finally {
    exec.shutdown();
}

modernCode:
try (var exec = Executors
        .newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor()) {
    var futures = tasks.stream()
        .map(exec::submit)
        .toList();
}
